dc_description_s: This data represents roads for Douglas County, Wisconsin in 2025. [Refinement of dataset ready for Network Analyst and routing. City of Superior, Douglas County and Forestry gas tax road Centerline datasets merged together to create a countywide feature class. Also included are the COS Snow Routes and COS Truck Routes, both of these routes have a field of data that gives their designation.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
